desc: Kick Defender's Waterproof Silicon Shoe Protectors help to keep your shoes dry and clean. These shoe protectors are made from a durable elastic material that can be stretched over the shoe to create a waterproof barrier between your shoe and the outside world.

layout.text: Dedicated to Clean and Dry Shoes
Here at Kick Defender™ we have dedicated ourselves to providing the public with a one of a kind product to help keep you shielded from soggy and stained shoes
